        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Create a keystore object</para>
<para>A keystore object is persistent across runtime. It is saved on local filesystem via a vlc keystore module (KWallet, SecretService, Apple Keychain Service ...).</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>to be released with <ref refid="group__keystore__public_1ga8353e78625fdff8100a625a02f096cd5" kindref="member">vlc_keystore_release()</ref></para>
</simplesect>
<parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>p_parent</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>the parent object used to create the keystore object</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>a pointer to the keystore object, or NULL in case of error </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
